input: [int | uint | buff | string-ascii | string-utf8], [int | uint | buff | string-ascii | string-utf8]
description: Compares two inputs (Inputs must be of the same type), returns true if INPUT-1 is greater than INPUT-2 and false otherwise.
Stacks 1.0, the > comparable types are int and uint.
Stacks 2.1, the > comparable types are expanded to include string-ascii, string-utf8 and buff.
